results.title: X-Men/Spider-Man (2008) #4
results.description: It all leads up to this! The past comes back to haunt the modern-day X-Men and Spider-Man- with a vengeance- as Sinister's scheme reaches its fruition. A new evil is unleashed on the world...one with some all-too-familiar qualities...one that even the combined might of Spidey and the X-Men may not be able to fight! If you wondered how this mini-series would affect the present-day Marvel Universe, wonder no more, True Believer!
